query: update tb_package set package_send_date = $1, package_receive_date = $2, package_weight = $3, package_deliveryperson_id = $4, package_type_id = $5, package_status_id = $6, package_sender_id = $7, package_receiver_id = $8, package_warehouse_id = $9, package_paytype_id = $10, package_payer_id = $11 where package_uuid = $12
